Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3617193\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3617193\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ymp1665702709794.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ymp1665702709794.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ymp1665702709794.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ymp1665702709794\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                          \n Function\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Function to include in the panel. A function can be a user-defined operation or a structure editor function, or it can represent a new line or a separator.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ymp1665702709794__section_w1890ab1b5b1_w1891ab1b5_w1892ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ymp1665702709794__table_d12992e1_d12993e1_d12994e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ymp1665702709794__table_d12992e1_d12993e1_d12994e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ymp1665702709794__table_d12992e1_d12993e1_d12994e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ymp1665702709794__table_d12992e1_d12993e1_d12994e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Separator</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ymp1665702709794__table_d12992e1_d12993e1_d12994e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Inserts a space into the pane, which can separate groups of related panel functions.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ymp1665702709794__table_d12992e1_d12993e1_d12994e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">New_Line</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ymp1665702709794__table_d12992e1_d12993e1_d12994e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Creates a new line in the panel, enabling panels to contain multiple lines of buttons. All subsequent functions appear on the new line.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ymp1665702709794__table_d12992e1_d12993e1_d12994e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Activate_operation</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ymp1665702709794__table_d12992e1_d12993e1_d12994e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Operation in the current form. If the form does not contain the named operation, the button is disabled.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ymp1665702709794__table_d12992e1_d12993e1_d12994e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">StructureEditorFunction</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ymp1665702709794__table_d12992e1_d12993e1_d12994e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Uniface structure editor function. Each function can only be used once in a panel.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ymp1665702709794__section_zv3_ntr_cxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d812485e157\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ymp1665702709794__p_d110441e1_d110442e1_d110443e1\">Each panel button represents a function or\n            operation that is activated when the user clicks it. For structure editor functions, the\n            glyph and text associated with the function are automatically displayed. For operations,\n            you must explicitly specify the glyph and message text to be associated with the\n            button.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ymp1665702709794__section_hg1_ptr_cxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d812485e166\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"ymp1665702709794__ul_gxr_ptr_cxb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ymp1665702709794__li_d42698e1_d42699e1_d42700e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"byf1705583062647.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/byf1705583062647.html\" title=\"Panels are global objects that are typically used to create toolbars for form components and application shells. They contain buttons to execute structure editor functions and activate component operations.\">Panels</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ffz1665703117029.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Message Text</a><p>Text of message to be used in place of the glyph or as a tooltip. This property is read-only, displaying a message that has the same name as the selected glyph.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617193\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617193\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Function Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Function Function to include in the panel. A function can be a user-defined operation or a structure editor function, or it can represent a new line or a separator. Value Description Separator Inserts a space into the pane, which can separate groups of related panel functions. New_Line Creates a new line in the panel, enabling panels to contain multiple lines of buttons. All subsequent functions appear on the new line. Activate_operation Operation in the current form. If the form does not contain the named operation, the button is disabled. StructureEditorFunction Uniface structure editor function. Each function can only be used once in a panel. Description Each panel button represents a function or operation that is activated when the user clicks it. For structure editor functions, the glyph and text associated with the function are automatically displayed. For operations, you must explicitly specify the glyph and message text to be associated with the button. Applies To Panels Related Links Message Text Text of message to be used in place of the glyph or as a tooltip. This property is read-only, displaying a message that has the same name as the selected glyph. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}